Executive Profile
John Laurens Troost  Independent Director, SharpSpring, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships49$21,008
Background

		Mr. John Laurens Troost, also known as Rens, served as a Partner and Chief Executive Officer of Virtual Clarity Limited. Mr. Troost served as Head of Platform Design & Core Technology Architecture at UBS, AG, where he oversaw initiatives spanning the introduction of Linux, Virtualization, post 9/11 IT business continuity, datacenter strategy and consolidation and savings initiatives. He served as Managing Partner of Surgam Technology Partners, Chief Technology Officer ... of NAME, Inc., Manager of Systems & Network Engineering at Moore Capital Management and Senior Systems Administrator at Lehman Brothers. He is a contributor to the development of the original standards for email attachments (MIME standard RFC). He has been an Independent Director of SharpSpring, Inc. since July 2010. He served as an Executive Director at UBS, AG. Mr. Troost holds a degree from Columbia University.Read Full Background




