John Laurens Troost

Age : 49Public asset : 64,906 USDLinked companies :  SharpSpring Inc 





Summary 



Mr. John L. Troost is President & Chief Technology Officer at Virtual Clarity Ltd.He is on the Board of Directors at SharpSpring, Inc. Mr. Troost was previously employed as Head-Platform Design by UBS AG, Senior Systems Administrator by Lehman Brothers, Inc., Manager-Systems & Network Engineering by Moor Capital Management LLC, Chief Technology Officer by North American Media Engines, Inc., Managing Partner by Surgam Technology Partners, Inc., and Director & Head-Platform Design by UBS AG (New York).He received his undergraduate degree from Columbia University.



