Individual




John Laurens Troost



Mr. John L. Troost is Independent Director at SharpSpring, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at SharpSpring, Inc. Mr. Troost was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer & Partner by Virtual Clarity Ltd., Senior Systems Administrator by Lehman Brothers, Inc., Managing Partner by Surgam Technology Partners, Inc., and Director & Head-Platform Design by UBS AG (New York). He received his undergraduate degree from Columbia University.



